episodes.title: Weird HISTORICAL Cults That Will Shock You
episodes.description:
Discover the weirdest cults in history and their shocking endings. From Jonestown tragedy, Heaven’s Gate suicide, and the terror of the Manson Family, to Aum Shinrikyo’s Tokyo subway attack—this video reveals the darkest, strangest, and most bizarre cult stories ever told. Perfect for fans of weird history, true crime, mystery, and disturbing cult documentaries. Learn how dangerous leaders manipulated followers, how these cults ended, and why their stories still haunt the world today.

#WeirdHistory #TrueCrime #Cults #DarkHistory #Mystery #Jonestown #HeavensGate #MansonFamily #AumShinrikyo #WacoSiege #StrangeHistory #CreepyCults
